<L>__{110 municipal stadium. outside. day. february 10, 1957.}
<A>__{the municipal stadium is crowded with people. there is a football game between two european teams. it is almost the end of the first half. from above to the right of the guest box, there is a very loud explosion. strips of flesh are hurled into the air. thick, white smoke ... there are screams of terror. the people try to move away in haste. they are shoving, pushing, bumping into one another ... then, calm returns. the sirens of the ambulances are heard. the stretcher, the dead carried away, scores of wounded.}
